        "# While Loops"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "gEuYbOU65U6x"
      },
      "source": [
        "A while loop is a pre-test loop, which means the condition is tested before each iteration, as shown in this flowchart\n",
        "![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
