      "source": [
        "An else clause can also be used with a for loop. \n",
        "\n",
        "The following example shows a program that uses for-in-range, together with an else clause to test a prime number.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "qMuLr3w8oFKG"
      },
      "source": [
        "n = int(input('Enter a positive number:'))\n",
        "if n==1:\n",
        "    print('1 is a composite.')\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    for i in range(2,n):\n",
        "        if n%i==0:\n",
        "            print(n,'is a composite.')\n",
        "            break\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        print(n,'is a prime.')"
      ],
